4) Formalize the seven-layer architecture as a refinement stack

You already have the conceptual stack. Make it a refinement relation:

Let L_j be layer j’s interface, then:

L_{j+1} \preceq L_j

meaning “layer j+1 is implemented using services of layer j and cannot violate its guarantees.”

This is exactly OS-style “kernel provides invariants for userland.”

